title: Clock Feedthrough Impulse Capture
summary: Oscilloscope screenshot showing clock-feedthrough impulse on VOUT while SCL toggles.

structured_data.description: Text indicates AVDD=5.5V and clock feedthrough impulse approximately 1.5 nV-s. Vertical scales shown are VOUT 5 mV/div and SCL 5 V/div. Horizontal scale is 1 us/div.
